{
  "stem": "4361.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, clearly, a romance , began but it began in-- in a very painful way because that afternoon, he invited the entire-- the entire group to go to some park near the river, which was a very famous park that we all went.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he kept telling us, talk, talk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We all spoke Romanian, and we-- we talked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it turned out that he himself was a Romanian Jew born in Iasi, 'Ias-i' as it's pronounced here, which was part of Romania where there was a terrible pogrom, I believe, in 1942.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But-- but he was in his youth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a young man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was about 26, I believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "While he was a student in Iasi, he became a Communist, very simple.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when in 1940, Bessarabia was ceded to Russia-- this was also that reward, that Vienna award where all kinds of things were going on, chopping up countries back and forth-- he went over to Russia because he was a Communist.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was an idealist, a Communist idealist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so now, when this war starts, he is in the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, we learned that he found out about his parents, about the pogrom, but nobody knew what happened to his family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "His name was-- I hope it still is-- Leonid Geller, Geller.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was looking for the Geller family, and nobody could tell him what happened to them, whether they perished in the pogrom, in the Iasi pogrom, or whether they were taken away because they were also-- the Romanians took people to Transnistria where they set them up in ghettos and so forth.",
      "word_count": 52
    }
  ],
